org.tensorics.core.resolve.resolvers

Interface Resolver<R,E extends Expression<R>>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - the type of the resolved type
    E - the type of the expression that can be resolved
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractResolver, BinaryOperationResolver, ConversionOperationResolver, CreationOperationResolver, TensoricScriptResolver, UnaryOperationResolver

    public interface Resolver<R,E extends Expression<R>>
    The version of a resolver, that has its type of objects which it can resolve given in its generic parameters in the class. This is useful for the usage in lower levels of the framework.
